item_description: A mace imbued with the power of thunder. Deals lightning damage.
A wand that unleashes a frosty blast of ice. Deals cold damage.
A lucky rabbit's foot that can grant bonuses in various situations.
A potion that restores health and vitality.
A shield that provides unparalleled protection against damage.
A powerful elixir that restores mana points.
A ring imbued with the power of dragons, increasing strength and agility.
A powerful talisman that grants increased health regeneration.
An ancient amulet with magical properties that grant various bonuses.
A staff that emits a bright light, increasing the wielder's magic power.
A heavy armor made of mithril plates, providing excellent protection.
A ring that increases the wearer's agility and movement speed.
A magical crystal ball that grants the ability to see into the future.
